Package: hilma
Type: Package
Title: An R package for accessing the Hilma API
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Markus Paasiniemi [aut]
Maintainer: Markus Paasiniemi <markus.paasiniemi@hansel.fi>
Description: The package allows users to fetch notices on public procurement in Finland
    from the public API at https://hns-hilma-prod-apim.portal.azure-api.net.
    The notices can be browsed at https://www.hankintailmoitukset.fi.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.0)
Imports:
    dplyr,
    glue,
    httr,
    lubridate,
    magrittr,
    purrr,
    stringr,
    tibble
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
Suggests: 
    testthat
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
